						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/Commodities/Biofuels/Related-developments/Kenya-plans-to-explore-alternative-sources-of-fuel" title="Kenya plans to explore alternative sources of fuel" alt="link">Kenya plans to explore alternative sources of fuel</a></h2>

	
					<p>During the height of the energy crisis, the Kenya Bio-Diesel Association (KBDA) was established in order to spearhead the search for alternative fuel so as to cushion the country from escalating oil prices. One such company that has ventured into biofuel crop production is Magadi Soda Company (MSC). Their goal is not only to empower the surrounding community but also to stimulate environmental conservation efforts (Source: Obadiah Ayoti, Africa Science News Service, 12 November 2008). </p>
							<p><span class="date">1/12/2008</span></p>
